{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"29879aa4f1","title":"北京市医药总公司关于对沈志庸问题的批复","origin":"根据文件翻印件打印。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"608d7a1700","index":0,"year":1979,"month":4,"day":28,"articleId":"29879aa4f1"}],"tags":[{"id":"aa9434abe4","name":"北京文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"75817f272f","type":"title","text":"北京市医药总公司关于对沈志庸问题的批复（沈志庸）","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29879aa4f1"},{"id":"679342e711","type":"appellation","text":"北京制药厂：","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29879aa4f1"},{"id":"19e9084040","type":"paragraph","text":"你厂“关于原教养人员沈志庸的复查报告”收悉。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29879aa4f1"},{"id":"679083fc70","type":"paragraph","text":"经研究鉴于沈志庸的右派问题已经改正，劳动教养问题朝阳分局已撤销，同志沈志庸返京入户，由北京制药厂重新安排工作，工资定为行政21级，62元。从78年10月开始执行。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29879aa4f1"},{"id":"a1104b3bda","type":"paragraph","text":" 北京市医药总公司一九七九年四月二十八日","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29879aa4f1"},{"id":"be05dc0a4b","type":"subtitle","text":"对沈志庸同志一九五八年划为右派分子的改正决定","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29879aa4f1"},{"id":"36527dd2b0","type":"subtitle","text":"1979.03.10","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29879aa4f1"},{"id":"17f5a1d278","type":"paragraph","text":"沈志庸，男，43岁，家庭出身职员，本人成份学生，原为物理系学生，共青团员。现在山西霍县王庄煤矿工作。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29879aa4f1"},{"id":"5ee1aca2db","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五八年沈志庸同志被划为资产阶级右派分子，予以劳动考察、开除团籍处分。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29879aa4f1"},{"id":"bd7a00b612","type":"paragraph","text":"现按照中共中央〔1978〕55号文件精神和一九五七年《中共中央关于“划右派分子的标准”的通知》的规定，进行复查，原划沈志庸为右派分子属于错划，现决定予以改正，并撤销对他的劳动考察、开除团籍处分。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29879aa4f1"},{"id":"5ac6ecaeec","type":"paragraph","text":"关于工作安排、工龄计算、工资待遇等问题，由现在所在地区县以上组织、人事、劳动部门按照中央五部“统发文〔1979〕第143号”文件规定办理。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29879aa4f1"},{"id":"0185a77a71","type":"paragraph","text":" 中共北京大学委员会一九七九年三月十日","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29879aa4f1"}],"page":{"id":"0772dac94d","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29879aa4f1","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}